						<li>Attired in airy aquatic apparel, Alex sets out for<br>her first-ever vacation alongside her dear friend<br>Elisanne. The sun shines at last on this girl once<br>veiled in darkness, lighting the way for her to<br>make irreplaceable summer memories.</li>
