				<span>Burning Bonds</span>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>Grants the user a strength amp, deals damage<br>to enemies in a line, and applies "Scorchbloom"<br>to them.<br><br>When Scorchbloom is lost, the affected enemy<br>will take damage and be inflicted with scorchrend.<br>Scorchbloom is lost when its remaining time is<br>depleted or when removed with the Tropical Snipe<br>skill, but it cannot be removed by attacks or effects<br>that dispel buffs.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 2,065 × 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 7,140<br>Special Effects:<br>・Scorchbloom<br>　　Lasts 30 seconds<br>　　Does not stack<br>　　Cannot be reapplied while active<br>Amps:<br>・Strength Amp (Team Amp MAX Lv. = 3)<br><br><color=#00008B>When Scorchbloom is Lost:</color><br>Damage: 1,432 × 1 hit<br>Special Effects:<br>・Scorchrend<br>　　Lasts 21 seconds<br>　　Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>　　Damage: 41.6<br></div></dd></dl></div>
