<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/71d793fb535ac808bdfe31e27ebe9b8b2.png"></span><span>Flurry Scorchrend Edge & Sting II</span></dt><dd><div>When the combo count is 15 or higher,<br>increases the chances of inflicting scorchrend<br>by 50% and its duration by 30%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/1a55c9cd31df1c438cd55d10b0a536742.png"></span><span>Sleep Res +100%</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to sleep by 100%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/71d793fb535ac808bdfe31e27ebe9b8b2.png"></span><span>Strength Amp = Scorchrend Edge & Sting II</span></dt><dd><div>When the user has a strength amp,<br>increases the chances of inflicting scorchrend<br>by 30% and its duration by 30%.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>・The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities, and represent the adventurer at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unlocked, not the stats when first obtained.</div><div>・Adventurers with the same name cannot be put into the same team.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div>2. Alberian Battle Royale skins for adventurers featured in this summon showcase will go on sale, and it will cost fewer items to unlock their skins. Note that some adventurers do not have adventurer skins.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1625032800,update_time1624930792